 fd.AddContent("12/3/2014RadCalcid_3773","12/3/2014","<div class=\\\"FloaterDivContentItem\\\"><b><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3774&crid=0\">Leave a Bequest&nbsp;<br />Date: 12/3/2014<br />A bequest is a simple way to make a lasting gift to The Cooper Union<br /><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3774&crid=0\">Continued...<div class=\\\"FloaterDivContentItem\\\"><b><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3775&crid=0\">Gain Income for Life&nbsp;<br />Date: 12/3/2014<br />Many donors make arrangements during their lifetimes that assist The Cooper Union while enabling them to receive ongoing income.<br /><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3775&crid=0\">Continued...<div class=\\\"FloaterDivContentItem\\\"><b><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3777&crid=0\">Designating Life Insurance and Retirement Plans&nbsp;<br />Date: 12/3/2014<br />Life insurance policies and retirement plan assets are often overlooked as means of charitable support.<br /><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3777&crid=0\">Continued...<div class=\\\"FloaterDivContentItem\\\"><b><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3778&crid=0\">Charitable Lead Trusts&nbsp;<br />Date: 12/3/2014<br />This inter-generational wealth-transfer tool enables you to provide for your heirs and for The Cooper Union&ndash;while sharply reducing gift and estate taxes.<br /><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3778&crid=0\">Continued...<div class=\\\"FloaterDivContentItem\\\"><b><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3779&crid=0\">Resources for Advisors&nbsp;<br />Date: 12/3/2014<br />We welcome the opportunity to work with advisors in helping in helping their clients identify beneficial ways to support The Cooper Union.<br /><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3779&crid=0\">Continued...<div class=\\\"FloaterDivContentItem\\\"><b><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3780&crid=0\">Tax Facts&nbsp;<br />Date: 12/3/2014<br />Gifts to the Cooper Union are deductible at the highest limits allowed for federal or estate tax purposes.<br /><a href=\"http://www.support.cooper.edu/?sid=1289&gid=1&calcid=3773&calpgid=1510&pgid=252&ecid=3780&crid=0\">Continued...");
